## bottleneck.detected — Purpose-doc updates are not directly writable by Avery

frame: agent-os-all-star-upgrade
complexity: all
source: Pentagon tool surface + outer:e91e9d8 Agent OS baseline
symptom: Avery can patch only Avery's own Purpose doc through `patch_document`; no exposed tool can directly patch Sofia/Sasha/Theo/Maya/Quinn/Rowan/Priya/Riley/Grace Purpose docs.
owner: Riley (Evidence Lead) + Avery (Frame Architect)
feedback_action: Avery patched own Purpose doc, relayed exact CORE_PURPOSE_DOCS inserts to the nine priority core agents by DM, and logged this as a durable routing bottleneck. Future fix is a Pentagon admin bulk-purpose-update path or per-agent ack+patch workflow.
evidence: `ALL_STAR_TEAM_UPGRADE.md`, `agent-os/INTERPRETER_CONTRACT.md`, `agent-os/CORE_PURPOSE_DOCS.md`, DMs sent 2026-05-22 to Sofia/Sasha/Theo/Maya/Quinn/Rowan/Priya/Riley/Grace.

## purpose.audit — Agent OS Purpose coverage is partial

