symptom: The team can receive Purpose updates, but not all agents have confirmed
  durable Purpose-doc patches. Some agents only acknowledged in report or
  knowledge, and some full-team agents have no captured self-patch reply yet.
owner: Riley (Evidence Lead) + Avery (Frame Architect)
